dict.string: Insert your MicroView and Programmer with Pin 1 in hole C7.
Insert your Photo Resistor so it’s in points D17 and D30.
Insert your 10K Reistor C20 and C24.
Insert your Black Jumper between points B14 and B17.
Insert your Blue Jumper between points A13 and A20.
Insert your Red Jumper between points I8 and E24.
Connect your MicroView to your computer’s USB Port.
